
1. (catkin_make)

Navigate to the pioneer3dx_wss file and catkin_make pioneer3dx, pioneer3dx_simulation, pioneer3dx_2dslam and pioneer3dx_map_and_nav


2.A. (CoppeliaSim)

In a seperate terminal use the source command:

source source_all.bash

Next to open the CoppeliaSim of the robot use the command:

roslaunch coppeliasim_p3dx_sim coppeliasim_p3dx_sim.launch


2.B. (RViz)

In a seperate terminal use the source command:

source source_all.bash

Next to open the RViz of the robot use the command:

roslaunch coppeliasim_p3dx_sim coppeliasim_p3dx_launch.launch




2.C. (SLAM)

In a seperate terminal update to use gmapping:

sudo apt-get update

Install the gmapping softwear:

sudo apt-get install ros-noetic-gmapping

As before use the source command:

source source_all.bash

And to open the RViz of the robot use the command:

roslaunch pioneer3dx_gmapping pioneer3dx_gmapping.launch


2.D. 




